adams.flow.control.Flow
	-annotation
	A simple for showing how to generate colors with a \ncolor provider and turning them into their hexa-decimal\nnotation.
	-actor
		adams.flow.source.ColorProvider
			-provider
				adams.gui.visualization.core.DefaultColorProvider
	-actor
		adams.flow.transformer.Convert
			-conversion
				adams.data.conversion.ColorToHex
	-actor
		adams.flow.sink.Display
			-writer
				adams.data.io.output.NullWriter
	-flow-execution-listener
		adams.flow.execution.NullListener

